  "title": "The 2017 Risk All Stars",
  "author": "R&I Editorial Team",
  "date_published": "2017-09-12",
  "body": "<html><body><div class=\"contents\">\n<div class=\"avtempclass\" id=\"post-thumbnail\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-post-image\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" height=\"525\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" src=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/AllStars2017-700-700x525.jpg\" srcset=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/AllStars2017-700.jpg 700w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/AllStars2017-700-250x188.jpg 250w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/AllStars2017-700-120x90.jpg 120w\" width=\"700\"/> </div>\n<h3><strong><a href=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/sharp-instincts/\">Sharp Instincts</a></strong></h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_GillianCummingsBeck.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full wp-image-36328 alignleft\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"150\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_GillianCummingsBeck.jpg\" srcset=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_GillianCummingsBeck.jpg 150w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_GillianCummingsBeck-120x120.jpg 120w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_GillianCummingsBeck-32x32.jpg 32w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_GillianCummingsBeck-50x50.jpg 50w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_GillianCummingsBeck-64x64.jpg 64w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_GillianCummingsBeck-96x96.jpg 96w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_GillianCummingsBeck-128x128.jpg 128w\" width=\"150\"/></a>Gillian Cummings-Beck: Director, Insurance &amp; Risk Management, Chico’s FAS Inc.</strong></p>\n<p>Chico’s risk manager wasn’t afraid to change important relationships.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3><strong><a href=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/captives-writ-larger/\">Captives, Writ Larger</a></strong></h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_CourtneyClaflin.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full wp-image-36320 alignleft\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"150\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_CourtneyClaflin.jpg\" srcset=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_CourtneyClaflin.jpg 150w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_CourtneyClaflin-120x120.jpg 120w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_CourtneyClaflin-32x32.jpg 32w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_CourtneyClaflin-50x50.jpg 50w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_CourtneyClaflin-64x64.jpg 64w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_CourtneyClaflin-96x96.jpg 96w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_CourtneyClaflin-128x128.jpg 128w\" width=\"150\"/></a>Courtney Claflin: Executive Director, captive programs, University of California</strong></p>\n<p>The University of California’s Courtney Claflin is putting on a clinic in captive management.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3><strong><a href=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/seeking-clarity/\">Seeking Clarity</a></strong></h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_Cring.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-36321\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_Cring.jpg\" srcset=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_Cring.jpg 150w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_Cring-120x120.jpg 120w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_Cring-32x32.jpg 32w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_Cring-50x50.jpg 50w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_Cring-64x64.jpg 64w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_Cring-96x96.jpg 96w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_Cring-128x128.jpg 128w\" width=\"150\"/></a>Faith Cring: Director, Engineering, Environmental, Safety and Insurance, Growmark Inc.</strong></p>\n<p>Faith Cring makes sure she educates underwriters about her agricultural cooperative’s risks. She also insists on complete transparency.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3><strong><a href=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/the-right-connections/\">The Right Connections</a></strong></h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_MichelleBennett.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-36331\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_MichelleBennett.jpg\" srcset=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_MichelleBennett.jpg 150w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_MichelleBennett-120x120.jpg 120w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_MichelleBennett-32x32.jpg 32w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_MichelleBennett-50x50.jpg 50w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_MichelleBennett-64x64.jpg 64w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_MichelleBennett-96x96.jpg 96w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_MichelleBennett-128x128.jpg 128w\" width=\"150\"/></a>Michelle Bennett: Director of Risk Management, Cable One</strong></p>\n<p>Cable One’s Michelle Bennett is very good at forming relationships, both inside and outside of her company.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/right-formula-claims-closure/\"><strong>The Right Formula for Claims Closure</strong></a></h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_KevinMoss.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-36330\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_KevinMoss.jpg\" srcset=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_KevinMoss.jpg 150w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_KevinMoss-120x120.jpg 120w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_KevinMoss-32x32.jpg 32w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_KevinMoss-50x50.jpg 50w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_KevinMoss-64x64.jpg 64w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_KevinMoss-96x96.jpg 96w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_KevinMoss-128x128.jpg 128w\" width=\"150\"/></a>Kevin Moss: Director, Casualty Insurance and Risk, Michelin North America Inc.</strong></p>\n<p>With diligent prep work and high emotional intelligence, Kevin Moss cut Michelin’s outstanding reserves nearly in half.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/seeing-opportunity-expansion/\"><strong>Seeing Opportunity in Expansion</strong></a></h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_SteveRichards.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-36333\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_SteveRichards.jpg\" srcset=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_SteveRichards.jpg 150w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_SteveRichards-120x120.jpg 120w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_SteveRichards-32x32.jpg 32w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_SteveRichards-50x50.jpg 50w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_SteveRichards-64x64.jpg 64w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_SteveRichards-96x96.jpg 96w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_SteveRichards-128x128.jpg 128w\" width=\"150\"/></a>Steve Richards: Director Claims &amp; Litigation, Coca-Cola Bottling Company Consolidated</strong></p>\n<p>Steve Richards masterfully recalibrated Coca-Cola’s workers’ comp program when the company rapidly added 25 locations and thousands of new employees.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3><strong><a href=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/risk-management-memory-care/\">Risk Management in Memory Care</a></strong></h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_FrankRusso.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-36327\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_FrankRusso.jpg\" srcset=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_FrankRusso.jpg 150w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_FrankRusso-120x120.jpg 120w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_FrankRusso-32x32.jpg 32w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_FrankRusso-50x50.jpg 50w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_FrankRusso-64x64.jpg 64w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_FrankRusso-96x96.jpg 96w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_FrankRusso-128x128.jpg 128w\" width=\"150\"/></a>Frank Russo: Senior Vice President, risk and legal affairs, Silverado Senior Living</strong></p>\n<p>Frank Russo integrated risk management throughout his company, building a strong and collaborative risk culture.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3><strong><a href=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/the-ergonomic-evaluator/\">The Ergonomic Evaluator</a></strong></h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_JosephMazza.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-36329\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_JosephMazza.jpg\" srcset=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_JosephMazza.jpg 150w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_JosephMazza-120x120.jpg 120w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_JosephMazza-32x32.jpg 32w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_JosephMazza-50x50.jpg 50w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_JosephMazza-64x64.jpg 64w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_JosephMazza-96x96.jpg 96w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_JosephMazza-128x128.jpg 128w\" width=\"150\"/></a>Joseph Mazza: Director of Risk Management and ADA Coordinator, MiraCosta College</strong></p>\n<p>Joseph J. Mazza has cut repetitive motion workers’ comp claims in half by training in ergonomics.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3><strong><a href=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/a-friend-of-the-business/\">A Friend of the Business</a></strong></h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_SimonArgent.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-36332\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_SimonArgent.jpg\" srcset=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_SimonArgent.jpg 150w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_SimonArgent-120x120.jpg 120w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_SimonArgent-32x32.jpg 32w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_SimonArgent-50x50.jpg 50w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_SimonArgent-64x64.jpg 64w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_SimonArgent-96x96.jpg 96w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_SimonArgent-128x128.jpg 128w\" width=\"150\"/></a>Simon Argent: Senior Vice President, Head of Credit Risk Management, XL Catlin</strong></p>\n<p>XL Catlin’s Simon Argent leads a team that is giving insurance business leaders much better insight into their credit and country risks.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3><strong><a href=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/persistence-pays-off/\">Persistence Pays Off</a></strong></h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_WallaceJones.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-36335\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_WallaceJones.jpg\" srcset=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_WallaceJones.jpg 150w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_WallaceJones-120x120.jpg 120w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_WallaceJones-32x32.jpg 32w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_WallaceJones-50x50.jpg 50w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_WallaceJones-64x64.jpg 64w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_WallaceJones-96x96.jpg 96w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_WallaceJones-128x128.jpg 128w\" width=\"150\"/></a>Wallace Jones: Director, Global Benefits &amp; Insurance, Ashley Furniture Industries</strong></p>\n<p>Wallace Jones achieved double-digit premium reductions for Ashley Furniture by educating senior leaders and implementing changes over a four-year period.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3><strong><a href=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/standing-up-and-standing-out/\">Standing Up and Standing Out</a></strong></h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_DanHolden.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-36326\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_DanHolden.jpg\" srcset=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_DanHolden.jpg 150w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_DanHolden-120x120.jpg 120w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_DanHolden-32x32.jpg 32w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_DanHolden-50x50.jpg 50w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_DanHolden-64x64.jpg 64w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_DanHolden-96x96.jpg 96w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_DanHolden-128x128.jpg 128w\" width=\"150\"/></a>Dan Holden: Manager, Corporate Risk &amp; Insurance, Daimler Trucks North America</strong></p>\n<p>Daimler Trucks North America’s Dan Holden advocated for a disaster recovery system that is now being implemented internationally.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3><strong><a href=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/unbridled-passion/\">Unbridled Passion</a></strong></h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_ZachFinn.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-36336\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_ZachFinn.jpg\" srcset=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_ZachFinn.jpg 150w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_ZachFinn-120x120.jpg 120w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_ZachFinn-32x32.jpg 32w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_ZachFinn-50x50.jpg 50w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_ZachFinn-64x64.jpg 64w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_ZachFinn-96x96.jpg 96w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_ZachFinn-128x128.jpg 128w\" width=\"150\"/></a>Zach Finn: Director, Davey Risk Management and Insurance program, Butler University</strong></p>\n<p>Butler University’s Zach Finn is tackling the risk management talent shortage head-on.</p>\n<p><strong> </strong></p>\n<h3><strong><a href=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/building-on-the-power-of-appreciation\">Building on the Power of Appreciation</a></strong></h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_TimLiberty.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-36334\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_TimLiberty.jpg\" srcset=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_TimLiberty.jpg 150w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_TimLiberty-120x120.jpg 120w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_TimLiberty-32x32.jpg 32w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_TimLiberty-50x50.jpg 50w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_TimLiberty-64x64.jpg 64w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_TimLiberty-96x96.jpg 96w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/09152017_1CS_AllStars_150_TimLiberty-128x128.jpg 128w\" width=\"150\"/></a>Tim Liberty: Senior Claims Consultant, Baldwin Krystyn Sherman Partners</strong></p>\n<p>Leveraging the adage “You catch more flies with honey,” Tim Liberty is giving his growing company a distinct competitive advantage.</p>\n<div class=\"bio\">The R&amp;I Editorial Team can be reached at <a class=\"__cf_email__\" data-cfemail=\"0e636b6a676f6d61607a6f6d7a4e7a666b67607d7a677a7b7a6b7d20617c69\" href=\"/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection\">[email protected]</a>.</div>\n<div class=\"pad-1\"> </div>\n<div class=\"actions\">\n</div>\n</div></body></html>",
